# Alice the Time Bender

Always read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root before editing.

## Stack

- Single file: `index.html` (inline CSS + JS)
- No build step, no `package.json`, no frameworks

## Rules

- Do not redesign or restyle unless the user explicitly requests it
- Do not split `index.html` into separate asset files
- Do not add npm dependencies or bundlers
- Preview with `python3 -m http.server 8000` or open `index.html` in a browser
- Brand palette: bone `#EDEBE7`, charcoal `#1A1A18`, black `#0b0b0a`, ochre `#B8923F`
